{"id":4270,"date":"2022-06-19T17:36:33","date_gmt":"2022-06-19T10:36:33","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/?p=4270"},"modified":"2022-06-19T17:36:33","modified_gmt":"2022-06-19T10:36:33","slug":"full-de-thi-ngu-van-minh-hoa-tham-khao-thi-that-tu-2017-den-2021","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/blog\/2022\/06\/19\/full-de-thi-ngu-van-minh-hoa-tham-khao-thi-that-tu-2017-den-2021\/","title":{"rendered":"Full \u0111\u1ec1 thi ng\u1eef v\u0103n (minh h\u1ecda, tham kh\u1ea3o, thi th\u1eadt) t\u1eeb 2017 \u0111\u1ebfn 2021"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Xin ch\u00e0o c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n, m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 Th\u1ecf v\u00e0 m\u00ecnh l\u1ea1i \u0111\u0103ng t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e2y! N\u1ebfu th\u1ea5y t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh hay ho th\u00ec c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n gi\u00fap m\u00ecnh chia s\u1ebb cho b\u1ea1n b\u00e8 v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e2n nha!<\/p>\n<p>Trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y, m\u00ecnh xin g\u1eedi t\u1edbi c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n b\u1ed9 si\u00eau t\u1eadp \u0111\u1ec1 thi m\u00f4n ng\u1eef v\u0103n c\u1ee7a B\u1ed9 gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o. Bao g\u1ed3m c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1 thi minh h\u1ecda, tham kh\u1ea3o v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1 thi th\u1eadt t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2017 \u0111\u1ebfn nay. M\u00ecnh ngh\u0129 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n luy\u1ec7n qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec1, c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u \u0111\u00e2u \u0111\u00e2u \u0111\u1ec3 \u00f4n. T\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t v\u1eabn c\u1ee9 l\u00e0 b\u00e1m s\u00e1t c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a B\u1ed9 Gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c!<\/p>\n<p>Trong m\u1ea5y ch\u1ee5c c\u00e1i \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y, m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec1 thi th\u1eadt n\u0103m 2018 l\u00e0 kh\u00f3 nh\u1ea5t. Ngo\u00e0i nh\u1eefng n\u1ed9i dung th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00e1c n\u0103m kh\u00e1c v\u1eabn c\u00f3, th\u00ec n\u0103m 2018 c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t n\u1ed9i dung l\u00e0 d\u1ea1ng ngh\u1ecb lu\u1eadn so s\u00e1nh gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c t\u00e1c ph\u1ea9m v\u0103n h\u1ecdc. Lo\u1ea1i n\u00e0y ngo\u00e0i kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng vi\u1ebft \u0111\u01a1n thu\u1ea7n, c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i v\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea3 k\u0129 n\u0103ng so s\u00e1nh, t\u01b0 duy ph\u1ea3n bi\u1ec7n,&#8230; v\u00e0o b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u1eefa. Kh\u00e1 l\u00e0 kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea5y! C\u00e1c b\u1ea1n l\u00e0m th\u1eed nha!<\/p>\n<p>Link t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y: <a href=\"https:\/\/drive.google.com\/drive\/folders\/1By6qhxVgbo33mJYQV3DIU5PFj8bXwKPv?usp=sharing\">T\u1ea0I \u0110\u00c2Y!<\/a><br \/>\nCh\u00fac c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n h\u1ecdc t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 cao trong k\u00ec thi s\u1eafp t\u1edbi nha!<\/p>\n<!-- AddThis Advanced Settings generic via filter on the_content --><!-- AddThis Share Buttons generic via filter on the_content -->","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<div class=\"mh-excerpt\"><p>Xin ch\u00e0o c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n, m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 Th\u1ecf v\u00e0 m\u00ecnh l\u1ea1i \u0111\u0103ng t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e2y! N\u1ebfu th\u1ea5y t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh hay <a class=\"mh-excerpt-more\" href=\"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/blog\/2022\/06\/19\/full-de-thi-ngu-van-minh-hoa-tham-khao-thi-that-tu-2017-den-2021\/\" title=\"Full \u0111\u1ec1 thi ng\u1eef v\u0103n (minh h\u1ecda, tham kh\u1ea3o, thi th\u1eadt) t\u1eeb 2017 \u0111\u1ebfn 2021\">[&#8230;]<\/a><!-- AddThis Advanced Settings generic via filter on get_the_excerpt --><!-- AddThis Share Buttons generic via filter on get_the_excerpt --><\/p>\n<\/div>","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":4271,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[13,5],"tags":[43,19],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4270"}],"collection":[{"